Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:48.44,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:48.44,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:54.78,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
