Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.83,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:08.17,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:08.17,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:15.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:15.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:21.56,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:21.56,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths of\Nhalf the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma's Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Will your father, Sovereign Degwin,\Nbe visiting Earth in the near future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard of any such plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If he visits, it would be\Na pleasure to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Garma always looks so gallant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- How elegant!\N- I'm going to faint!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand these fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd all be in a panic if they knew\Nabout the Trojan Horse and its mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We can't build\Nan anti-Trojan Horse task force...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...since the front lines\Nare stretched too thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma. Who's that gentleman over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are a number of ways\Nof dealing with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The former mayor, Eschönbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He hates Zeon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's stayed here to watch over\Nthe civilian population.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a stubborn old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Presenting Icelina Eschönbach!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh my.\N- How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really, now...\N- Quite the beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Romance on the front lines, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Garma, the spoiled rich kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he cannot let his daughter\Nmarry a son of the Zabi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...which reigns over the Zeon forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly sounds like your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about Zeon\Nor the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Icelina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you, even if\Nit means betraying my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to betray\Nmy father and Zeon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I have a chance to capture\Nsome important Federation secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If that goes well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...even my father will surely grant me\Nmy impossible wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he still denies me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I am prepared\Nto abandon Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Garma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, excuse me...\N- Never mind that. Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse has reached the S-3 point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If they pass this last defensive line...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...they'll escape into Federation airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another defensive line there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be headed there myself\Nwith a mobile squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Inform Lt. Commander Char.\NMobilize!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I capture the Federation's\Nnew weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll bring them to the homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeon forces won't let us out of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But if things continue like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take a forward position\Nand act as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That won't work. It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's shown up on our sound detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy formation\Napproaching from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any Gaws?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's accompanied by fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's all the more reason!\NI can lure them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the White Base can escape to the sea\Nin the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Luring them away\Nand breaking through...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There, in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a domed baseball stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yes, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Hide the White Base in there.\NIt should fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid being detected by the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base will cease all operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll watch their movements, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I disagree! If we do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, in the Gundam.\NKai, in the Guncannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu and Hayato, standby in the Guntank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that\Nwe still have civilians on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a civilian too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All crew standby at level 1 battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a sound\Nuntil I give further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay in your rooms, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Turn about, 180 degrees!\N- Aye, sir! Turning 180 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing? If we're going to die,\Nwe might as well leave the ship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If we escape into the city, we can survive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it this far. Please stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put our hearts together\Nand fight as one, we will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, don't shine that light on him. Honestly!\N- There there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Give him to me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you don't have to cry anymore. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My baby! My baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I looked away for one second\Nand we got separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Patrol Lugguns! What do you mean,\Nyou can't find the Trojan Horse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't left the city!\NSearch harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to flush out a rat in a hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...is with a bit of carpet bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. All units! Deploy roller shifts\Nand commence bombing immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a miracle if we didn't get hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Someone! Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The young mistress is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!\NThere's no way that you could understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress. Going now would be\Nlike going to your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, you must not...!\NYour father is calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you! You ill-mannered brutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress! Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somewhere I need to be!\NNow let go of me! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say to my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I hear the son of Zeon's leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...wants to marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you can't deny me my freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the right to choose my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Icelina have the keys to the jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Has the Trojan Horse come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it? Why won't it come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're starting to understand\Nthe art of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have to go down and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want to do,\NI'll go down with my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Would you really do that for me?\N- Of course I would. You are my superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, perhaps... but you served\Ndirectly under my older brother, Dozle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem unusually agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty for glory just because of a girl.\NTry to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So he thinks I'm anxious\Nbecause of Icelina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Char.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inform me as soon as you seee suits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll destroy them with the Gaw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored that you came to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you request.\NGood luck, Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,May the glory of victory be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright, three Zakus are coming down.\NThey're headed directly this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Amuro, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakus are approaching. Move the Gundam\Naway from the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll go with your battle plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lure the Zakus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...and, if possible, the main enemy forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...into the area in front of the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then we'll strike withs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guntank and Guncannon,e White Base as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that misleading soldiers\Non my own side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...doesn't sit too well with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. That mobile suit should be\Nout of the Trojan Horse by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's there! The enemy is near!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned mobile suit is getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good try, mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to lure us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would mean...\Nthe Trojan Horse is behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's a pretty good plan.\NLet me use it for my own revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been waiting, Char.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse is ahead!\NCan you pursue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready beam cannons!\NAll units, standby for attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright. The enemy fighters are moving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Mirai. Get back in position.\NWe're going to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank! Guncannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All White Base gunners!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Coordinate your targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire barrage in 10 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}10...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}8... 7... 6...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}5... 4... 3...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}2... 1...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy fire from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Trojan Horse!\NAttacking from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Climb! Climb right now!\N- Not possible, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn about, 180 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ram the Gaw into the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma, if you can still hear me,\Nblame this on the misfortune of your birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Misfortune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- That's right! Misfortune!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a good friend to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is the one to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! You planned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a man of the Zabi family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My death will not be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One enemy aircraft heading for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...! They're going to ram us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! Climb! Climb now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency ascent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to the Principality of Zeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, you did well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our breakthrough plan worked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will escape now. Return to ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, what's wrong?! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand! Returning to ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I will inform my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Icelina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Icelina, Garma has apparently died in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city-state which calls itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...floats on the far side of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,News of the death of Garma, the Zabi family's\Nyoungest son, has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Degwin Zabi, the Sovereign of\Nthe Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the father of Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...couldn't help dropping his cane\Nbefore the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no end to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma's remaining forces\Nlaunch a vengeful assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With Ryu in the Guncannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro tries to destroy the Gaw, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...a beautiful girl stands in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her trembling hands clutch a gun\Naimed at Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Icelina - Love's Remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Icelina - Love's Remains
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:54.24,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:59.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:09.46,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:14.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:19.02,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.40,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.98,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:39.29,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:54.24,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:59.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:09.46,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:14.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:19.02,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.40,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.98,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:39.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
